<p><span style="font-family: COURIER;"><span style="font-size:2.5em;"><strong>CONFIDENTIAL</strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:1em;">ORGANIZATION FOR THE RECLAMATION OF ISLAMIC ARTIFACTS</span><br />
<span style="font-size:1em;">SHEMIRAN, TEHRAN PROVINCE</span><br />
<span style="font-size:1em;">ISLAMIC REPUBLIC OF IRAN</span></p>
</div>
<br />
<hr />
<table>
<tr>
<td><span style="color: white"><sub>بسم الله</sub></span></td>
<td>FROM:</td>
<td><span style="color: white"><sub>الرحمن الرحيم</sub></span></td>
<td>Chairman Mehdi Bazargan [JIBRIL ACTUAL]</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="color: white"><sub>بسم الله</sub></span></td>
<td>TO:</td>
<td><span style="color: white"><sub>الرحمن الرحيم</sub></span></td>
<td>All Field Commander-Level Officers, All Facility Commander-Level Officers</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="color: white"><sub>بسم الله</sub></span></td>
<td>SUBJ:</td>
<td><span style="color: white"><sub>الرحمن الرحيم</sub></span></td>
<td>Regarding Current Political Instabilities</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="color: white"><sub>بسم الله</sub></span></td>
